{
  "stem": "21310.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so-- and then we left, and-- with that threat that if he hears once more that she is making some new rumors.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When we came down, his bicycle was covered with flowers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because the Poles, you know, they saw a German come with us, a German officer.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as I mentioned, the windows were open.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all that yelling, and they all hated her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because apparently she was a woman in the neighborhood who always would denounce people of any infraction, not only Jews but other things.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So-- so that's about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And soon after that, I think he was-- he was sent to Yugoslavia or somewhere.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But, you know, when I tell people that I went to a German officer to tell him, I'm being accused of being Jewish, help me, it's quite-- so I had that story.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I-- I mean I-- there's so many.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The one-- one story I do want to say is-- or tell, is when I-- I wanted to make some extra money.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so on weekends, I got an extra job selling tickets.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The whole line there, where the railroad was, was little resort towns.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And people would come for a weekends or come for just a Saturday or Sunday, and-- and spend money, get drunk, and then on the way back when they were buying the tickets, and the ticket was-- I forgot what it was.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But let's say it was like $1, the equivalent of a $1 or $0.80, so they would throw a dollar.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I would get-- you know, and not take the-- the-- the money, the $0.20.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "No, leave it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So not only did I make extra money getting paid, but I also made extra money from what was left from the tickets.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
